e to represent a road or the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"path along which something moves.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape","abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" is an abstract class that represents a shape or annotation. Shapes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"constitute the content of a map — not only the overlays atop the map, but also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the content that forms the base map.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"MLNShape","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShape","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource":{"title":"MLNShapeSource","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown on the map. The shapes may be instances of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or they may be defined by local or external"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON"},{"type":"text","text":" code. A shape source is added to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the shape source. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can update a shape source by setting its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"URL"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:imageForAnnotation:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns an annotation image object to mark the given point annotation object on"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:imageForAnnotation:"}],"type":"topic","title":"mapView:imageForAnnotation:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:imageForAnnotation:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:imageforannotation:","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:imageForAnnotation:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"topic","title":"MLNPointCollection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"disconnected vertices, specified as "},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"orchard."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointCollection","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolygon":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolygon"}],"title":"MLNPolygon","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object represents a closed shape consisting of four or more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"vertices, specified as ","type":"text"},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instances, and the edges that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollectionFeature":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollectionfeature","title":"MLNPointCollectionFeature","type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollectionFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object associates a point collection with an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"optional identifier and attributes."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollectionFeature","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPointCollectionFeature"}]}}}